            <p>Sell tickets right from your event’s Epilogger page! Show potential attendees the fantastic community already involved.</p>
        </td>
        <td><img src="/Public/images/Upgrade/icon-featurecheckmark.png" alt="" class="benefitImageCheck" /></td>
        <td><img src="/Public/images/Upgrade/icon-featurecheckmark.png" alt="" class="benefitImageCheck" /></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td>
            <img src="/Public/images/Upgrade/icon-feature-toptweeters.png" alt="" class="benefitImage" />
            <h2>Top 10 Contributors</h2>
            <p>Recognize who has been talking about your event online the most with our top ten list.</p>
        </td>
        <td><img src="/Public/images/Upgrade/icon-featurecheckmark.png" alt="" class="benefitImageCheck" /></td>
        <td><img src="/Public/images/Upgrade/icon-featurecheckmark.png" alt="" class="benefitImageCheck" /></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td>
            <img src="/Public/images/Upgrade/icon-feature-uploadphoto.png" alt="Upload photos and albums" class="benefitImage" />
            <h2>Upload Photos & Albums</h2>
            <p>Make your event archive the most comprehensive by allowing your attendees to upload their own photos directly from <strong>Facebook, Flickr, or their computer</strong>.</p>
        </td>
        <td><img src="/Public/images/Upgrade/icon-featurecheckmark.png" alt="" class="benefitImageCheck" /></td>
        <td><img src="/Public/images/Upgrade/icon-featurecheckmark.png" alt="" class="benefitImageCheck" /></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td>
            <img src="/Public/images/Upgrade/icon-feature-commenting.png" alt="" class="benefitImage" />
